incident_updates.body: As part of our responsibilities for Web Hosting filerz, we will be performing infrastructure maintenance. This may temporarily affect availability. Start time : 20/10/2025 21:00 UTC End time : 21/10/2025 04:00 UTC Service impact : Concerned Filerz will be temporarily unavailable for 40 minutes during the maintenance. Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy, we will be performing an update for the storage servers hosting your data. This version brings improvements to certain security mechanisms, as well as some performance enhancements. List of concerned Filerz: - filerz969: Cluster026 - filerz1878: Cluster010 - filerz499, filerz1918: Cluster003 - filerz1809: Cluster031 - filerz1975: Cluster028 - filerz1924: Cluster017 - filerz1988: Cluster030

As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our Web Hosting offer. This may temporarily affect on configuration tasks. Start time : 21/10/2025 20:00 UTC End time : 21/10/2025 22:00 UTC Service impact : configuration tasks on clusters may experience slowness due to this maintenance https://web-cloud.status-ovhcloud.com/incidents/s5kjmxms8y6x Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy, we will be doing a maintenance on our clusters. Thank you for your understanding.
